<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= language === 'zh' ? 'zh-TW' : 'en' %>">
<head>
<!-- meta attributes -->
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="author" content="Jack Gowan">
<meta name="description" content="first built maze">
<title>The Maze - The Cavern Spirit</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/a_maze_style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 class="main-title"><%= translations?.[language]?.title || 'The Caverns' %></h1>

  <div class="room-container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="room-image">
        <img src="/images/a5_maze-cavern-2.png" alt="The caverns">
      </div>
      <div class="room-content">
    <div class="room-text">
      <code>
            <%- translations?.[language]?.text || `You wonder through the crystal caverns, searching. Crystalline formations glow with inner light, casting prismatic patterns. The air hums with magical power.
        <p> But something isn't quite right. Havent you been here before?</p>
        <p> There is a feeling that ahead is something dangerous and way above your level.</p>
        <p>Maybe you got it wrong perhaps there is another way to go.</p>` %>
          </code>
    </div>

    <hr/>

    <div class="navigation">
          <p><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.prompt || 'You continue on but with doubts:' %></p>
          <a href="/maze/ghost-pre3"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[0] || 'You still keep moving' %></a>
          <a href="/start_0"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[1] || 'maybe head back to the start of the maze' %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>